aker level 3. You have at least 5+ years of relevant work experience in B2B sales 4. Working experience in overseas (outside China) sales management is preferred 5. Able to lead a team independently 6. Your sales skills includes: a. strategic sales planning b. pipeline management c. relationship building d. digital market knowledge e. negotiation skills f. presentation skills g. analytical skills h. people management i. creative and bold sales strategy j. You have strong experience and knowledge in one or more of the following: -complex technical sales for B2B -cloud or large enterprise sales solutions Skills Sales Compensation TBD ", 
